data.description: Carlisle township, KEYSTONE SCHOOLS! Make sure to stop by for a tour of this spacious, attractive home! A welcoming entryway features an adorable, rustic coat closet, which flows right into the large 17x13 family room. Dining room has a nice open feel. Kitchen has been renovated recently with newer/brand new stainless steel appliances, leathered granite countertops & stylish painted cabinets. Massive 21x13 living room featuring hardwood floors, a wood-burning fireplace and large windows that drench the space in natural light. The sunroom adds such a versatile element to the main floor. Upstairs you'll find a fantastic spacious 16x11 master bedroom with walk-in closet and connecting full bathroom. Two additional 12x11 bedrooms (with huge closets!) complete the second story. The basement is partially finished with a 13x12 flex space & attached 10x9 closet. Additionally in the lower level: the laundry room & storage/mechanical room. The backyard is fully fenced and boasts a patio with pergola, beautiful firepit, above-ground pool & attached deck, as well as a 10x16 shed. XL driveyway. BRAND NEW AIR CONDITIONER! NEW ROOF! Don't miss this one!
